  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To assess in moderate to severe Obstructive Sleep Apnea the effects of one year therapy with
      nighttime continuous positive airway pressure ventilation on the prevalence of metabolic
      syndrome and cardiovascular damage.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
